{"tid":1961534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[中伊友好]  伊朗衛生部發言人稱中國疫情數據是“慘痛的笑話”","createTime":"2020-04-07T00:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T08:22:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8395e32a2cbd5f77c76ecbf394ecc05a99a54ead","tid":1961534,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:28:02.000Z","msg":"伊朗衛生部發言人稱中國疫情數據是&ldquo;慘痛的笑話&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/iran-official-calls-chinas-coronavirus-numbers-a-bitter-joke-20200406/5362676.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Firan-official-calls-chinas-coronavirus-numbers-a-bitter-joke-20200406%2F5362676.html&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=4aac269f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/iran-official-calls-chinas-coronavirus-numbers-a-bitter-joke-20200406/5362676.html</a><br />\n<br />\n伊朗衛生部發言人賈漢普爾（Kianush Jahanpur）日前批評了中國的疫情數據，將中國政府公佈的新冠疫情數字描述為一個&ldquo;慘痛的笑話&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n賈漢普爾星期日（4月5日）表示，中國官方的統計數據似乎是一個&ldquo;慘痛的笑話&rdquo;（bitter joke），讓世界上許多人認為新冠病毒就像流感一樣，且死亡率更低。<br />\n<br />\n他還表示：&ldquo;如果中國說疫情在兩個月內得到了控制，人們應該認真考慮一下。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據英國《衛報》報導說，他的推文引來了中國駐伊朗大使常華的責備。常華表示中國每天都會舉行新聞發布會，賈漢普爾應該仔細關注中國的數據再做結論。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n似乎是受到了來自中國的壓力，伊朗外交部發言人阿巴斯&middot;穆薩維（Abbas Mousavi）當天晚些時候在推特上表達了對中國的感謝，&ldquo;中國在抗擊疫情中展現的勇敢、奉獻和專業精神應該得到感謝&rdquo;，&ldquo;在這些艱難時刻，伊朗一直感謝中國&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n賈漢普爾此後也表揚了中國，他星期一在推特上寫到，&ldquo;在這一困難時期，中國對伊朗人民的支持令人難忘。&rdquo;他還說，伊朗政府和人民都很感激在疫情中與他們站在一起的國家。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗受疫情影響非常嚴重，截止星期一，伊朗累計確診60500新冠病例，共3739人死於新冠病毒。"},{"pid":"257bd0e397f42e93443535c4b5cc3e536cb2150e","tid":1961534,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dd70bd9859266b8cbcda713918db2fbd142ebc","tid":1961534,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8a3204b7fb1d006ba7ec9ff7e7be7f320ed467","tid":1961534,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:43:17.000Z","msg":"弱智到咁好難幫你架喎"},{"pid":"bf3eb3897c6084425612308dc3690e905123a521","tid":1961534,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:44:47.000Z","msg":"屌你玩隱瞞<br />\n我收番"},{"pid":"9b58024560fa8a1228b0c50f7b11bb8ae980e9eb","tid":1961534,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6fb0a26ca48a4a406b0954e8a9cf0e11e2663d","tid":1961534,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:48:30.000Z","msg":"盟友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c819f5c4966b5d2a13f61e7f49af0ec476501c31","tid":1961534,"uid":325869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T00:50:12.000Z","msg":"跳出跳入... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6265dbb6ecaeb2f8a10153cbc2297c328724d949","tid":1961534,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:0